  <div id="text-content_25429210-1E48-0135-C7F0-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can add or edit the amount of points on a given assignment.</p>
<p><strong>Notes</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>When an assignment is set as a moderated assignment, only the moderator or a Canvas admin can edit the assignment after it is published.</li>
<li>Points possible must be set to a number greater than zero for assignments with percentage, points, letter grade, or GPA grading types.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

